race.comment: SANCTUARY STORM (2) returned in good order with a close-up second here at this circuit and the step-up to the mile looks ideal. Only needs some luck getting across from the wide draw to be playing a key role in the finish. PRIDE OF SAVABELLA (4) saluted over this course and distance last time out and can go right on with the job now. High on confidence now and has top-three aspirations. MAMMOTH MOUNTAIN (19) has hit the top-five in seven of his past eight starts and is usually thereabouts. One for the exotics players at odds. SAVVY BEE (14) will be cherry-ripe fit for this and rounds out the selections.
